een domains. PVT operates as a plug-in layer for any dialogue synthesis pipeline, providing real-time feedback on both correctness and naturalness. This approach fundamentally shifts value tagging from a static annotation tool to a dynamic, cognitively-grounded quality assurance mechanism. By integrating pragmatic reasoning into the core tagging process, PVT reduces not only explicit errors but also subtle, socially implausible outputs that degrade user trust in synthetic agents. Applications include high-fidelity data augmentation, robust evaluation benchmarks, and safer training of open-ended dialogue models, particularly in safety-critical domains like healthcare or finance.",
